{"word":"διαζώννυμι","slug":"διαζώννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαζώννυμι</b></el> <el>(or <el>-ύω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ζώσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to gird round the middle</i>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to gird oneself with</i>, <el>ἐσθῆτα</el>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>διεζωσμένοι</el> <i>wearing drawers</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to engirdle, encompass</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}